The paper discusses the design of AI systems for managing employees in organizations, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses issues related to fairness and justice, which could fall under the categories of cybersecurity and privacy (cs.CY), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
